profile:
Vineuve is a family run construction company that provides a variety of construction services from building new homes from the ground up, to repurposing and renovating spaces that are apart of existing homes, offices, and other structures. In any case, each job is an opportunity to create something new with our clients. We bring our expertise, our industry know-how, our highly skilled and hard working team, & our community based values; we invite you to bring us your vision for your space. 

Let’s build together.

profile:
Integrity Builders Ltd has been building quality homes, renovations and additions in the Victoria area since 2004. Projects have included custom homes, basement renovations, kitchen and Bath remodels, commercial kitchens, as well as several group homes. No project is too big or too small. Integrity Builders is a licensed builder registered with the Home Owner Protection office and can provide new home warranty coverage through Travelers Canada.

We’re thrilled that you’re considering us for your renovations and additions! With Integrity Builders, no project is too difficult to complete. We enjoy the challenges we might face and we strive to give you the best results possible.

Are you ready to complete the renovations and additions you’ve always wanted? Integrity Builders is ready to help you make those dreams come true! Contact us today to get started on improving your house to finally reach the perfect home you’ve been waiting for.
services:
New Home Construction
Major Renovations 
Additions
Kitchen and Bath renovations
